  "bodyHtml": "<p><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"><strong>PRICING</strong><br><br>CCBM pricing is based on a per order-line-item model. CCBM costs will be issued every 10 days with your Back Market invoices, but the price-per-item will be fixed monthly (see indicator details below) for better financial planning. The price-per-item will include all costs — care, reverse logistics, packaging, etc. <br><br>The CCBM pricing model was created with 3 seller-centric tenets in mind: </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"><br><strong>1. Predictability:</strong> We’re giving you full transparency on all invoiced amounts — no hidden costs or fees! <br><strong>2. Simplicity: </strong>We’re making everything easier for you by consolidating multiple services and leveraging well-known and actionable indicators in the pricing grid<br><strong>3. Engagement: </strong>We’re rewarding you for quality and sales volume <br><br>The pricing is determined by the following 3 indicators: </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">1. Item category because weight impacts return shipping costs</span></p>\n<ul><li><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">Accessory, small, medium, and large item orders will be invoiced at different costs. The table below shows examples of each category, see the full list attached. Bulky items are excluded from crossborder returns, and will be invoiced like small items. Bulky items for France-France flows will be invoiced as large items beginning on November 5th. </span></li></ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">  </span></p>\n<table border=\"1\"><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"><strong>Category</strong></span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"><strong>Examples</strong></span></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">Accessory<br>(no automatic returns)</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">Smartphone Accessories, Earphones, MacBook chargers, Sim Card, Tablet Cases &amp; Protections, etc. </span></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">Small</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">Smartphones, Tablets, Apple Earphones, Cameras, Watches, etc.</span></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">Medium</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">MacBook, Office laptops, Gaming computers, Fans, Video Game consoles, Chromebooks, etc. </span></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">Large</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">Microwaves, Air purifiers, Televisions, Desktops, PC monitors, Electric Bikes, Printers, etc. </span></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">Bulky</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">Televisions, PC monitors, Electric Bikes, Ovens, Fridges, etc.</span></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><br><br><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"><strong>2. Quality </strong>(via the Long Term Contact Rate) to reward best-in-class sellers</span></p>\n<ul><li><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">The Long Term Contact Rate (LTCR) is an indicator used to estimate the number of customers’ requests in a given period. It is very closely related to a seller’s quality metrics. The LTCR is calculated as the proportion of contacts to orders within a 30-day period, <strong>see below: </strong></span></li></ul>\n<h3><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"><img alt=\"Screenshot 2022-07-01 at 16.01.44.png\" src=\"/ssc/servlet/rtaImage?eid=ka0aT000000PmRF&amp;feoid=00N3X00000M5fJO&amp;refid=0EM3X000008cvMZ\"></img></span></h3>\n<p>*After-sales tickets categorized with below reasons are excluded from LTCR computation:</p>\n<p> </p>\n<ul><li>Changed_Mind</li><li>Others</li><li>Delivery specifically related to PARCEL_RECOVERY_ISSUES, ADDRESS_ISSUE, and PICKUP_POINT_ISSUE</li></ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"><strong>3. Volume</strong> to incentivize growth on Back Market and create a fair distribution<br><br>Each month, we will look at the LTCR on the last day of the previous month and the average sales revenue of the past 3 months to determine the options for price-per-item. The product category will then be used to define the final  price-per-item of each order-line-item. <br><br><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Below is the CCBM pricing grid, which was created using the above tenets and indicators. To read the grid, consider your average monthly GMV and average LTCR. For example, a EU-seller who makes more than 1 million € of GMV a month (on average over the last 3 months) and has an LTCR below 5% will be invoiced at (taxes excluded):</span><br></span></p>\n<ul><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">€0.99 for accessories</span></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">€1.99 for small products</span></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">€2.99 for medium products </span></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">€4.99 for large products</span></li></ul>\n<table style=\"border-color: #000000;border-style: solid;width: 100.058%;height: 455.602px;\" border=\"1\"><thead><tr style=\"height: 35.0463px;\"><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;width: 10.6479%;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size: 13px;\">Seller tier</span></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;width: 21.298%;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size: 13px;\">Criteria</span></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;width: 24.7561%;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size: 13px;\">Product category</span></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;width: 11.7569%;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size: 13px;\">Low (&lt;5%)</span></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;width: 20.3312%;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size: 13px;\">Medium (&gt;5% &amp; &lt;9%)</span></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;width: 11.2099%;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size: 13px;\">High (&gt;9%)</span></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr style=\"height: 35.0463px;\"><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"4\" style=\"border-color: #000000;width: 10.6479%;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size: 13px;\">GOLD</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"4\" style=\"border-color: #000000;width: 21.298%;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size: 13px;\">&gt;1M GMV / month</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-color: #000000;width: 24.7561%;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size: 13px;\">Accessory</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\